nt to say in retort to your assumption that i do it all on purpose or.. whatever... im not sure what Smiles&#039; loss would damage. i wa sthe only person who ever interracted. pretty sure no one else wil leve notice.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429170816";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3345dd";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14291708135";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#1f89e2";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1325972;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1325972";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Black_Mage";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"333";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:4:"Jitz";s:4:"text";s:237:"really, though, im sick of people sneering at me all the time for being unhappy about unhappy things. im sorry im not an indestructible ice cold rhinoceros carved out of marble. just becuase you feel nothing doesnt mean no one else does.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429170936";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#3345dd";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14291709330";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#1f89e2";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1325973;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1325973";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"71";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Jitz";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"269";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:10:"Black_Mage";s:4:"text";s:197:"Shard and everyone close to Shard and who interact with her. Brookes would be pretty screwed, she has nobody else in her life and she&#039;s not exactly happy, herself. And she cared about Smiles. ";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1429170943";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#502cf0";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14291709467";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#8211f7";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1325976;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1325976";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:2:"91";s:6:"handle";s:10:"Black_Mage";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"333";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:4:"Jitz";s:4:"text";s:22:"fair enough, i suppose";s:9:"timestamp";s: